data.title: Pinky and the Brain
data.meta_description: The dynamic duo of the Animaniacs crew, Pinky and the Brain might look similar, but that's where their similarities end. Opposites attract as they say, and we couldn't pick a more perfectly contrasting frame for these two dudes! These furry friends were made out of 11 security envelopes.  Wall or Tabletop Display.
data.text:
This collage was drawn, cut and assembled by hand, using only repurposed security envelopes. Artwork is 5x7 and ready to be displayed in a vintage 7.5x10in brown and gold frame.

This is an original, one of a kind work of art.
